title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Bottom Dollar Bounties
content:
With crime statistics in Los Santos reaching stratospheric highs and the convictions hitting new lows, someone’s gotta round up the runners.

Meet Jenette, Maude Eccles’ daughter and the mind behind Bottom Dollar Bail Enforcement. She’s looking for a partner with ambition to catch felons on the lam.

Justice has its own reward in this town, and that reward is cold, hard cash. Bottom Dollar Bounties is now available.
